author: PlayStation
description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/code-vein-ii/

From weapons and partners to dungeons and bosses – join us on a deep dive into the Sunken Pylon and learn how it feels to play CODE VEIN II.

A Character Creator Demo has been announced! This demo will include the Character Creator with 64 slots, transferable to the full game. Players will be able to enjoy the hot spring in MagMell Institute and use Photo Mode to capture their newly created characters! The demo will be available on 1/23.

Bound By Blood – CODE VEIN II releases January 30th, 2026.
